experiences.description:
Vale produces the best quality iron ore in the world and your mission is: To transform natural resources into prosperity and sustainable development. 

The main responsibility is remain the available of automation in Iron Ore beneficiation plant. 
Develop and make changes in logic on SDCD system (800xA System - ABB Vendor); 
Develop and make changes in screens of SDCD system (800xA System - ABB Vendor); 
Maintenance in SDCD hardware (AC800M); 
Maintenance in field network (Profibus DP/PA and ModbusTCP); 
Maintenance in Ethernet Network; 
Maintenance in Wireless Network; 
Maintenance in communications interface of levels 2 (“SDCD by OPC) and 3 (“LIMS and MES” by OPC) in the industry automation pyramid; 
Responsible for intern projects; 
Projects are managed with PMBOK methodology from PMI institute.

